metadata.description:
Giant Swan is a an artist using Virtual Reality tools to create digital worlds experienced through image, video, 3d, print media and sculpture 

Artist Note: The 11:32 Absent-Express. 

We're all on some sort of journey, this one just happens to be mundane. 

Created Alongside a series of unique prints: Gyclee print on archival paper, sculpted in VR Hp Design Jet 06100 with HP original Viver inks 2400px, 100% cotton Italian textured paper.

Exhibited at CADAF 2020
metadata.name: The 11:32 Absent-Express
